E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263baed1b-49ed-411b-9df9-75bf34bb5217%5C%22%3EAt%20first%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20a%20COVID-19%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20we%20moved%20in%202020%2C%20the%20state%20virtually%20shut%20down%20because%20of%20COVID-19.%20As%20things%20started%20to%20open%20up%20again%2C%20we%20tried%20to%20establish%20care%20with%20primary%20care%20doctors%20and%20specialists.%20Getting%20in%20as%20a%20new%20patient%20was%20a%20mixed%20bag%3B%20I%20got%20an%20OB-GYN%20pretty%20quickly%2C%20but%20it%20took%20over%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdermatologist-doesnt-use-filler-anti-aging-what-she-does-instead-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esee%20a%20dermatologist%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20figured%20wait%20times%20would%20eventually%20start%20going%20back%20to%20normal%2C%20but%20that%20was%20not%20the%20case.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-shares-tips-for-being-heard-during-medical-visits-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGetting%20in%20touch%20with%20our%20pediatrician%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20still%20a%20Herculean%20effort%2C%20with%20hour-long%20waits%20on%20the%20phone%20and%20days%20going%20by%20before%20our%20calls%20are%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20our%20kids%20are%20older%20and%20can%20verbalize%20if%20something%20is%20wrong%2C%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Furgent-care-vs-emergency-room%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etake%20them%20to%20urgent%20care%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20they're%20sick%20instead%20of%20trying%20their%20pediatrician.%20When%20I%20mentioned%20this%20recently%20to%20a%20group%20of%20friends%2C%20many%20said%20they%20were%20doing%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20specialist%20care%20is%20also%20still%20a%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202024%2C%20I%20made%20an%20appointment%20to%20see%20if%20I%20