%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22England%20Great%20Identifies%20Indian%20Cricket's%20Ronaldo.%20Not%20Kohli%20Or%20Sachin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20England%20fast%20bowler%20Steve%20Harmison%20has%20drawn%20a%20striking%20parallel%20between%20India's%20ace%20pacer%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20football%20superstar%20Cristiano%20Ronaldo%2C%20emphasising%20the%20irreplaceable%20nature%20of%20the%20fast%20bowler.%20Harmison%20believes%20that%20if%20Bumrah%20is%20forced%20to%20miss%20the%20upcoming%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20due%20to%20injury%2C%20it%20would%20be%20akin%20to%20a%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20without%20Ronaldo%20at%20his%20peak.%20Bumrah%2C%20who%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20India's%20Test%20series%20against%20Australia%2C%20is%20struggling%20with%20a%20swelling%20on%20his%20back%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20miss%20the%20group%20stage%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Harmison%20insists%20that%20India%20should%20keep%20him%20in%20the%20squad%20until%20the%20last%20possible%20moment%20in%20hopes%20of%20his%20return%20for%20the%20knockout%20rounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20TalkSport%20Cricket%2C%20Harmison%20made%20a%20compelling%20case%20for%20India's%20patience%20with%20their%20premier%20fast%20bowler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20Jasprit%20Bumrah.%20For%20me%2C%20you%20can't%20replace%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20anytime%2C%26quot%3B%20Harmison%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20would%20even%20go%20up%20to%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20final%20to%20take%20him%20that%20far%20because%20he's%20Jasprit%20Bumrah.%20He's%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world.%20That%20would%20be%20my%20take%20from%20an%20Indian%20point%20of%20view.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20England%20pacer%20likened%20Bumrah's%20potential%20absence%20to%20a%20football%20World%20Cup%20without%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20forwards%20of%20all%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20going%20to%20a%20football%20World%20Cup%20without%20your%20best%20striker%2C%20Cristiano%20Ronaldo.%20Fifteen%20years%20ago%2C%20you%20don't%20replace%20Ronaldo%20until%20you%20have%20to.%20That's%20what%20I%20imagine%20India%20will%20do%20with%20Bumrah.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarmison%20even%20joked%20that%20India%20could%20%E2%80%9Ccarry%20him%20around%20in%20a%20sedan%20chair%E2%80%9D%20throughout%20the%20tournament%20and%20hope%20that%20he%20is%20available%20by%20the%20semi-finals%20or%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%2014-man%20squad.%20That's%20good%20enough%20to%20get%20me%20through%20the%20group%20games.%20We%20might%20get%20him%20by%20the%20semifinal%2C%20more%20than%20the%20semifinal.%20If%20he's%20not%20fit%2C%20we'll%20replace%20him%20just%20in%20case%20we%20have%20another%20injury.%20But%20he's%20Jasprit%20Bumrah.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Champions%20Trophy%20is%20set%20to%20begin%20on%20February%2019%2C%20featuring%20the%20world's%20top%20eight%20ODI%20teams.%20India%20will%20play%20all%20their%20matches%20in%20Dubai%20due%20to%20their%20refusal%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20prompted%20the%20ICC%20to%20approve%20a%20hybrid%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20group-stage%20campaign%20includes%20matches%20against%20Bangladesh%20(February%2020)%2C%20Pakistan%20(February%2023)%2C%20and%20New%20Zealand%20(March%202).%20If%20India%20progresses%2C%20the%20semi-finals%20will%20take%20place%20on%20March%204%20and%205%2C%20with%20the%20final%20set%20for%20March%209.%20Whether%20Bumrah%20will%20be%20ready%20by%20then%20remains%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20was%20in%20sensational%20form%20during%20India's%20recent%20five-match%20Test%20series%20in%20Australia%2C%20where%20he%20bagged%2032%20wickets%20and%20was%20named%20Player%20of%20the%20Series.%20However%2C%20he%20sat%20out%20the%20final%20day%20of%20the%20series%20in%20Sydney%20due%20to%20his%20back%20injury%2C%20as%20Australia%2