y%20regions.%20The%20coil%20configuration%20is%20especially%20notable%20around%20the%20perimeter%2C%20where%20a%20higher%20concentration%20of%20springs%20lends%20extra%20edge%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20latex%20hybrid%20is%20available%20in%20all%20standard%20sizes%20from%20twin%20to%20California%20king%20plus%20full%20XL.%20I%20tested%20the%20queen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad40c335-7b2c-40bd-b664-baa13eab82a3%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%20of%20the%20My%20Green%20Mattress%20Kiwi%20Organic%20Mattress%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20My%20Green%20Mattress%20Kiwi%20Organic%20Mattress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22My%20green%20mattress%20kiwi%20bed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67aa78c67bb3f854015c6cfb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECombined%20with%20a%20latex%20comfort%20layer%20and%20individually%20wrapped%20springs%20for%20support%2C%20the%20Kiwi%20offered%20balanced%20spinal%20alignment%20and%20pressure%20relief%20where%20I%20needed%20it%20most.%20%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cac89251-39e6-431c-8241-06a5a2284779%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Setup%5C%22%3ESetup%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unboxing%20experience%20of%20the%20My%20Green%20Mattress%20Kiwi%20Organic%20was%20similar%20to%20other%20beds%20in%20a%20box.%20At%2085%20pounds%20for%20the%20queen%2C%20the%20bed%20requires%20a%20two-person%20setup%20%E2%80%94%20a%20factor%20worth%20considering%20when%20planning%20your%20delivery%20logistics.%20While%20My%20Green%20Mattress%20doesn't%20include%20setup%20instructions%20or%20a%20cutting%20tool%2C%20the%20process%20is%20intuitive%3A%20simply%20position%20the%20compressed%20mattress%20on%20your%20foundation%20and%20remove%20the%20vacuum-sealed%20packaging.%20I%20managed%20to%20remove%20the%20plastic%20by%20hand%2C%20though%20having%20scissors%20nearby%20would%20streamline%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mattress%20expanded%20rapidly%20once%20freed%20from%20the%20plastic%2C%20achieving%20full%20height%20within%20minutes.%20Off-gassing%20was%20minimal%2C%20with%20only%20a%20mild%20initial%20odor%20that%20dissipated%20by%20bedtime%20%E2%80%94%20a%20testament%20to%20its%20natural%20materials.%20One%20notable%20limitation%20is%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20white-glove%20delivery%20service%2C%20meaning%20those%20requiring%20setup%20assistance%20must%20make%20other%20arrangements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213c8a551-eb45-4c2d-963b-7cb2e266fc75%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Comfort%5C%22%3EComfort%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20slept%20on%20the%20Kiwi%20Organic%20Mattress%20for%2031%20nights%20and%20found%20its%20%26quot%3Bmedium%26quot%3B%20firmness%20rating%20accurate%2C%20registering%20at%20about%205%20out%20of%2010%20on%20my%20firmness%20scale%20(with%2010%20being%20the%20firmest).%20As%20a%20side%20sleeper%20weighing%20230%20pounds%20at%206%20feet%20tall%2C%20I%20experienced%20consistent%20comfort%20across%20multiple%20sleep%20positions.%20However%2C%20my%20sleep%20tracking%20data%20revealed%20slightly%20lower%20quality%20scores%20than%20my%20baseline%20(61%20versus%20my%20typical%2063%2C%20as%20measured%20by%20my%20Garmin%20watch).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mattress%20showed%20impressive%20versatility.%20It%20accommodated%20my%20primary%20side-sleeping%20preference%20while%20remaining%20comfortable%20during%20occasional%20stints%20on%20my%20stomach%20and%20back.%20The%20surface%20offered%20balanced%20spinal%20alignment%20and%20pressure%20relief%2C%20though%20I%20noted%20sporadic%20shoulder%20stiffness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20my%20experience%2C%20I%20recommend%20the%20Kiwi%20Organic%20for%20most%20sleep%20styles%2C%20especially%20those%20seeking%20a%20medium-feel%20mattress.%20Yet%2C%20heavier%20individuals%20(over%20230%20pounds)%20who%20primarily%20sleep%20on%20their%20back%20or%20stomach%20may%20benefit%20from%20a%20firmer%20surface%20for%20optimal%20support.%20The%20bed%20strikes%20an%20effective%20balance%20between%20support%20and%20sink%2C%20though%20individual%20comfort%20experiences%20may%20vary%20based%20on%20sleep%20preferences%20and%20body%20type.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22897f68a6-3b87-473c-971c-1727f19ac7f9%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Heat%20dissipation%5C%22%3EHeat%20dissipation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20my%20trusty%20laser%20thermometer%2C%20I%20tracked%20how%20well%20the%20Kiwi%20Organic%20Mattress%20handled%20heat%20throughout%20the%20night.%20The%20data%20tells%20an%20interesting%20story%3A%20when%20I%20got%20up%20each%20morning%2C%20the%20surface%20averaged%2090%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20%E2%80%94%20just%20a%20touch%20warmer%20than%20typical%20mattresses%2C%20which%20usually%20hit%20about%2089.5%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20cooling%20down%2C%20the%20mattress%20performed%20right%20at%20the%20average.%20After%20getting%20up%2C%20the%20temperature%20dropped%20by%2012%20degrees%20within%20two%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20exactly%20what%20we%20see%20with%20most%20mattresses.%20The%20organic%20wool%20and%20coil%20design%20should%20theoretically%20aid%20in%20cooling%2C%20but%20I%20had%20some%20warmer%20nights%20where%20heat%20retention%20was%20definitely%20noticeable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20tend%20to%20feel%20cold%20at%20night%2C%20you'll%20probably%20appreciate%20how%20this%20mattress%20holds%20onto%20a%20bit%20of%20warmth.%20But%20if%20you're%20a%20hot%20sleeper%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20either%20look%20at%20specifically%20designed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-cooling-mattress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecooling%20mattresses%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20plan%20to%20add%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-cooling-products-for-better-sleep%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecooling%20accessories%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20make%20it%20work%20for%20you.%20The%20heat%20retention%20isn't%20dramatic%2C%20but%20it's%20something%20to%20consider%20if%20temperature%20affects%20your%20sleep%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22169be3d0-17ae-47bd-b580-22881f80b128%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Edge%20support%5C%22%3EEdge%20support%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221341%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20measures%20how%20much%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20My%20Green%20Mattress%20Kiwi%20sags%20when%20he%20sits%20on%20it.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a66e4e7bb3f854015c3bc2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221006%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20edge%20support%20of%20the%20Kiwi%20Organic%20Mattress%20isn't%20horrible%2C%20but%20I%20expected%20better.%3Cp%3EErin%20Brains%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ran%20two%20tests%20to%20measure%20edge%20support%2C%20which%20matters%20if%20you%20share%20a%20bed%20or%20often%20sit%20on%20the%20edge.%20First%2C%20I%20did%20a%20simple%20sitting%20test%20with%20a%20yardstick%20to%20measure%20how%20much%20the%20edge%20sinks.%20Then%2C%20I%20checked%20stability%20by%20lying%20on%20the%20edge%20and%20slowly%20rolling%20outward%20(think%20of%20it%20like%20trying%20to%20reach%20something%20on%20your%20nightstand).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20edges%20compressed%20more%20than%20I'd%20like.%20When%20sitting%2C%20they%20sank%204.5%20inches%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20notably%20deeper%20than%20the%203-inch%20sink%20I%20usually%20see%20in%20beds.%20During%20my%20roll-off%20test%2C%20I%20could%20lean%20just%20past%20a%2045-degree%20angle%20before%20losing%20stability%20%E2%80%94%20not%20terrible%20but%20not%20great%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20surprised%20me%20was%20that%20the%20edge%20support%20wasn't%20more%20robust%20despite%20having%20tighter%20coils%20along%20the%20perimeter.%20While%20it's%20not%20a%20dealbreaker%2C%20it's%20worth%20considering%20if%20you're%20shopping%20for%20a%20smaller%20size.%20If%20edge%20support%20is%20high%20on%20your%20priorities%2C%20I%20recommend%20buying%20a%20larger%20size%20to%20give%20yourself%20a%20more%20stable%20sleeping%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3f5e355-d423-4cae-8139-134f5e779413%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Motion%20isolation%5C%22%3EMotion%20isolation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221341%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20drops%20a%20bowling%20ball%20on%20the%20My%20Green%20Mattress%20Kiwi%20to%20test%20its%20motion%20isolation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a671d56630eb10385bfab2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221006%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20My%20Green%20Mattress%20Kiwi%20had%20great%20vibrometer%20readings%20when%20I%20dropped%20a%20bowling%20ball%20on%20it.%3Cp%3EErin%20Brains%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20check%20if%20you'll%20feel%20your%20partner%20moving%20around%20at%20night%2C%20I%20ran%20two%20tests.%20First%2C%20I%20got%20technical%20with%20it%20%E2%80%94%20using%20a%20vibrometer%20(think%20of%20it%20as%20a%20super-sensitive%20motion%20detector)%20on%20one%20side%20of%20the%20bed%20while%20dropping%20a%20bowling%20ball%20on%20the%20other%20side%20to%20simulate%20someone%20moving.%20The%20readings%20showed%20that%20the%20Kiwi%20Organic%20Mattress%20absorbs%20movement%20better%20than%20most%20mattresses%20I've%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20double-check%20these%20results%20in%20a%20real-world%20scenario%2C%20I%20had%20my%20wife%20roll%20around%20on%20one%20side%20while%20I%20lay%20still%20on%20the%20other.%20I%20barely%20felt%20any%20movement.%20Combining%20individually%20wrapped%20coils%20and%20those%20cushy%20layers%20of%20latex%20and%20wool%20really%20does%20a%20great%20job%20of%20keeping%20motion%20contained.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20or%20your%20partner%20toss%20and%20turn%20or%20get%20up%20during%20the%20night%2C%20this%20mattress%20should%20help%20keep%20those%20disruptions%20to%20a%20minimum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e52e9e45-6219-46c6-bec8-849dc503ed16%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Trial%20period%20and%20warranty%5C%22%3ETrial%20period%20and%20warranty%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20Green%20Mattress%20provides%20a%20365-night%20sleep%20trial%2C%20which%20is%20much%20more%20generous%20than%20the%20industry%20standard.%20However%2C%20you%20need%20to%20keep%20the%20mattress%20for%20at%20least%2030%20nights%20before%20initiating%20a%20return%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20their%20mandatory%20%26quot%3Bbreak-in%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20designed%20to%20let%20your%20body%20fully%20adjust%20to%20the%20new%20sleep%20surface.%20If%20you%20decide%20to%20return%20it%2C%20you%20must%20coordinate%20with%20My%20Green%20Mattress%20to%20donate%20the%20unwanted%20bed%20to%20a%20local%20charity%20and%20supply%20donation%20documentation%20to%20receive%20your%20refund.%20While%20they%20refund%20your%20full%20purchase%20price%2C%20they%20don't%20cover%20donation%20costs%20or%20return%20shipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20warranty%20coverage%20spans%2020%20years%2C%20which%20is%20notably%20longer%20than%20the%20typical%2010%20years.%20Yet%2C%20there's%20some%20fine%20print%20to%20consider%3A%20Only%20the%20first%2010%20years%20provide%20full%20coverage%2C%20while%20years%2011-20%20run%20prorated%2C%20meaning%20you'll%20pay%20an%20increasing%20percentage%20of%20the%20replacement%20cost%20as%20time%20passes.%20The%20warranty%20covers%20manufacturing%20defects%20and%20sagging%20over%201.5%20inches%20%E2%80%94%20fairly%20standard%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22029cd8f1-312f-4671-ba0a-9fa6221a3d16%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20edge%20support%20fell%20short%20of%20expectations%2C%20with%20a%204.5-inch%20compression%20that%20exceeds%20the%20typical%203%20inches%20in%20my%20testing.%20This%20is%20especially%20noticeable%20when%20sitting%20or%20lying%20near%20the%20perimeter%2C%20potentially%20limiting%20the%20usable%20sleep%20surface%20%E2%80%94%20a%20significant%20consideration%20for%20couples%20sharing%20smaller%20mattress%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETemperature%20regulation%20was%20inconsistent%20during%20my%20testing.%20While%20not%20a%20major%20concern%2C%20hot%20sleepers%20may%20need%20extra%20cooling%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20white-glove%20delivery%20service%20presents%20a%20logistical%20challenge%2C%20especially%20considering%20the%20larger%20sizes%20can%20get%20quite%20hefty%20%E2%80%94%20a%20California%20king%20is%20120%20pounds.%20While%20the%20mattress%20is%20delivered%20to%20your%20door%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20arrange%20setup%20assistance%20and%20handle%20the%20somewhat%20cumbersome%20unboxing%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20heavier%20individuals%2C%20especially%20those%20over%20230%20pounds%20who%20prefer%20stomach%20or%20back%20sleeping%2C%20the%20medium%20firmness%20level%20may%20not%20offer%20adequate%20support%20for%20optimal%20spinal%20alignment%2C%20potentially%20necessitating%20a%20firmer%20sleep%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22054ad2f5-607a-4662-a7d3-d5f5abbe3d3a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20other%20mattress%20for%20adults%20offered%20by%20My%20Green%20Mattress%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mygreenmattress.com%2Fproduct%2Fnatural-escape%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENatural%20Escape%20Organic%20Mattress%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20about%20%24400%20more%20expensive%20than%20the%20Kiwi%20and%20features%20the%20same%20materials%20and%20certifications.%20However%2C%20the%20Natural%20Escape%20packs%20in%20more%20pocket%20coils%2C%20has%20a%20three-inch%20latex%20layer%20as%20opposed%20to%20the%20Kiwi's%20two-inch%2C%20a%20firmer%20feel%2C%20and%20is%20designed%20to%20hold%20a%20highe