20falling%20to%20Jofra%20Archer%20for%2015.%20However%2C%20with%20Virat%20Kohli%20returning%20to%20the%20XI%20for%20the%20second%20game%2C%20the%2022-year-old%20was%20immediately%20dropped%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20his%20role%20in%20India's%20long-term%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%2C%20speaking%20on%20his%20YouTube%20show%2C%20stated%20that%20India's%20top-order%20is%20looking%20stable%20with%20Rohit%20Sharma%20back%20in%20form%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%20as%20vice-captain%2C%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20an%20immovable%20presence.%20He%20further%20added%20that%20Shreyas%20Iyer's%20match-winning%2059%20off%2036%20balls%20in%20the%20first%20ODI%20had%20potentially%20reshaped%20India's%20approach%20to%20squad%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20batting%20order%20is%20looking%20set.%20Rohit%20has%20started%20scoring%20runs.%20Shubman%20Gill%20is%20our%20vice-captain%2C%20and%20he%20is%20in%20good%20form.%20Virat%20Kohli%20will%20eventually%20return%20to%20form.%20Even%20if%20he%20doesn't%2C%20god%20forbid%2C%20India%20are%20not%20going%20to%20drop%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShreyas%20Iyer%20is%20at%20No.%204.%20At%20No.%205%2C%20whether%20it's%20KL%20Rahul%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%20or%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20the%20slot%20is%20settled.%20One%20of%20the%20two%E2%80%94Rahul%20and%20Pant%E2%80%94will%20have%20to%20be%20left%20out.%20And%20then%20you%20have%20an%20extra%20batter.%20You%20might%20not%20require%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal.%20That's%20a%20possibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20hinted%20that%20India%20initially%20wanted%20a%20left-right%20combination%20in%20the%20top%20order%20but%20have%20seemingly%20abandoned%20that%20approach%20after%20Iyer's%20impact%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20wanted%20to%20maintain%20a%20left-right%20combination%20in%20the%20batting%20order.%20Now%2C%20you%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it.%20You%20have%20played%20your%20hand%2C%20and%20that%20has%20backfired%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Bumrah's%20availability%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20still%20uncertain%2C%20Chopra%20suggested%20that%20Siraj%20could%20find%20a%20way%20back%20into%20the%20squad.%20Siraj%20was%20not%20included%20in%20the%20ODI%20squad%20against%20England%20or%20the%20preliminary%20Champions%20Trophy%20squad%2C%20but%20his%20experience%20could%20be%20crucial%20if%20India%20requires%20three%20frontline%20fast%20bowlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20play%20Yashasvi.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20can't%20play%20him%2C%20why%20take%20him%20to%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%3F%20I%20think%20Mohammed%20Siraj's%20chances%20of%20playing%20are%20higher%20than%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal's%2C%26quot%3B%20Chopra%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20see%20a%20strong%20chance%20for%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20to%20be%20included%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20feel%20the%20need%20for%20experience%20in%20the%20bowling%20attack%20against%20Pakistan.%20You%20might%20want%20to%20go%20in%20with%20three%20fast%20bowlers%E2%80%94Siraj%20could%20come%20in.%20Then%2C%20Yashasvi%20might%20have%20to%20make%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20strike%20bowler%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20who%20sustained%20a%20back%20injury%20during%20the%20final%20Test%20of%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20in%20January%2C%20is%20currently%20undergoing%20rehabilitation%20at%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy%20(NCA)%20in%20Bengaluru.%20While%20he%20was%20named%20in%20India's%20preliminary%20squad%2C%20his%20participation%20hinges%20on%20a%20final%20fitness%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739278260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fivd68ito_gautam-gambhir-and-ajit-agarkar-afp_625x300_27_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsp