02024%20via%20its%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20trend%20has%20drawn%20the%20format%20closer%20to%20the%20daytime%20and%20late-night%20talk%20shows%20that%20have%20been%20on%20TV%20for%20decades%2C%20said%20Vox%20Media's%20SVP%20and%20general%20manager%20for%20audio%20and%20digital%20video%20Ray%20Chao.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChao%20said%20that%20TV%20companies%20other%20than%20Netflix%20had%20already%20sought%20out%20talk%20shows%20that%20began%20in%20the%20digital%20realm.%20He%20pointed%20to%20Pat%20McAfee%20at%20ESPN%20and%20%26quot%3BHot%20Ones%26quot%3B%20at%20Hulu.%20Chao%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20Vox%20Media's%20active%20business%20opportunities%20in%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223104%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smartless%20hosts%20Jason%20Bateman%2C%20Will%20Arnett%2C%20and%20Sean%20Hayes%20sitting%20on%20a%20white%20couch.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67aa6a8deb4be2fff9a42c28%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222070%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20SmartLess%20podcast%20%E2%80%94%20hosted%20by%20Jason%20Bateman%2C%20Will%20Arnett%2C%20and%20Sean%20Hayes%20%E2%80%94%20spawned%20a%20tour%20docuseries%20on%20Max.%3Cp%3ECindy%20Ord%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20SiriusXM%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20insiders%20say%20more%20streamers%20entering%20the%20fray%20could%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20the%20podcast%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPodcasting%20has%20sort%20of%20been%20through%20a%20lot%20the%20last%2018%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PAVE%20Studios%20founder%20Max%20Cutler%2C%20citing%20Apple's%20iOS%2017%20update%2C%20which%20changed%20podcast%20downloads%20and%20impacted%20ads.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20someone%20like%20Netflix%20come%20in%20will%20really%20help%20grow%20the%20overall%20pie%20of%20listenership%20and%20viewership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2fcec9b-3788-45f6-90a6-2bef2920a0bf%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20Netflix%20want%3F%3C%2Fh2%