day%2C%20the%20judgment%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPest%20control%20companies%20found%20that%20insulation%20in%20the%20ceiling%20was%20the%20source%20of%20the%20issue.%20The%20works%20to%20replace%20the%20insulation%20cost%20%C2%A3270%2C000%2C%20the%20hearing%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20claimants%20accused%20Woodward-Fisher%20of%20knowingly%20selling%20the%20house%20with%20the%20moth%20infestation.%20He%20was%20found%20to%20have%20known%20about%20the%20issue%20since%20early%202018%20but%20failed%20to%20inform%20Patarkatsishvili%20and%20Hunyak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCpKv7vVIHr0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCpKv7vVIHr0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCpKv7vVIHr0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Iya%20Patarkatsishvili%20(%40iaiayo)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWoodward-Fisher%20told%20the%20court%20he%20had%20been%20informed%20that%20moths%20were%20not%20vermin%20and%20%26quot%3Btherefore%20not%20relevant%20to%20this%20inquiry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20ruled%20that%20Patarkatsishvili%20and%20Hunyak%20should%20be%20refunded%20much%20of%20the%20house's%20cost%2C%20minus%20%C2%A36%20million%20for%20the%20time%20they%20lived%20there%2C%20plus%20substantial%20damages.%20Woodward-Fisher%20was%20ordered%20to%20pay%20the%20couple%20%C2%A34%20million%20in%20damages%2C%20including%20%C2%A315%2C000%20for%20their%20moth-damaged%20clothes%20and%20%C2%A33.7%20million%20they%20paid%20in%20stamp%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Webber%2C%20an%20attorney%20at%20the%20firm%20Squire%20Patton%20Boggs%20who%20represented%20Patarkatsishvili%20and%20Hunyak%2C%20said%20the%20couple%20%26quot%3Bhope%20the%20case%20will%20serve%20as%20a%20warning%20to%20unscrupulous%20property%20developers%20who%20might%20seek%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20buyer%20beware%20to%20sell%20properties%20by%20concealing%20known%20defects%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20Guardian%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatarkatsishvili%20is%20a%20theater%20director.%20Her%20father%2C%20who%20died%20in%20the%20UK%20in%202008%2C%20was%20once%20Georgia's%20richest%20man%20worth%20%2412%20billion%2C%20per%20Forbes.%20Some%20of%20his%20assets%20passed%20to%20Patarkatsishvili.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWoodward-Fisher%20is%20a%20former%20rower%20who%20competed%20for%20the%20UK%20in%20the%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHorbury%20Villa%20was%20built%20in%20the%20mid-1800s%20and%20spanned%202%2C800%20sq%20ft.%20After%20being%20extended%2C%20the%20property%20covered%2011%2C000%20sq%20ft%20and%20featured%20a%20pool%2C%20spa%2C%20cinema%20and%20gym%20in%20the%20newly%20created%20basement%2C%20according%20to%20the%20website%20of%20architect%20Anthony%20Paine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20hr