enefit%20the%20world.%20AI%20must%20be%20about%20people-centric%20applications.%20We%20must%20address%20concerns%20related%20to%20cyber%20security%2C%20disinformation%2C%20and%20deep%20fakes%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20as%20leaders%20from%20across%20the%20world%20listened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20stressed%20on%20innovation%20and%20how%20%26quot%3BAI%20can%20help%20transform%20millions%20of%20lives%26quot%3B.%20This%20he%20said%20can%20be%20done%20in%20the%20fields%20of%20%26quot%3Bhealthcare%2C%20education%2C%20agriculture%2C%20and%20science.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20%26quot%3BAI%20can%20also%20help%20create%20a%20world%20in%20which%20the%20journey%20to%20sustainable%20development%20goals%20become%20easier%20and%20faster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20technology%20to%20be%20effective%20and%20useful%20for%20humankind%2C%20it%20must%20be%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20local%20ecosystems%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BAI's%20most-feared%20disruption%20is%20'loss%20of%20jobs'.%20But%20history%20has%20shown%20that%20work%20does%20not%20disappear%20due%20to%20technology.%26quot%3B%20He%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20nature%20of%20jobs%20change%20with%20time%2C%20and%20new%20types%20of%20jobs%20are%20created.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20noted%20that%20to%20address%20the%20concern%20of%20job%20losses%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20invest%20heavily%20on%20skilling%20and%20re-skilling%20of%20our%20people%20for%20an%20AI-driven%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20also%20said%20that%20AI%20needs%20to%20be%20sustainable.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20high-energy%20intensity%20of%20AI%20needs%20to%20be%20scrutinised.%20This%20will%20require%20green%20power%20to%20fuel%20its%20future.%20India%20and%20France%20have%20formed%20the%20International%20Solar%20Alliance%20in%20order%20to%20harness%20the%20Sun%20to%20ensure%20there%20is%20plenty%20green%20energy%20supply%20for%20future%20technologies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConservation%20of%20energy%20is%20key%20for%20the%20future%20of%20AI%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20giving%20the%20example%20of%20a%20human%20brain.%20%26quot%3BA%20human%20brain%20can%20do%20everything%20from%20poetry%20to%20complex%20mathematics%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20energy%20needed%20even%20by%20an%20ordinary%20light%20bulb.%26quot%3B%20That%20is%20what%20the%20AI%20revolution%20must%20aim%20for%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EINDIAN%20ADVANCES%20IN%20AI%20TECH%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20AI%20revolution%20in%20India%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20successfully%20built%20a%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%20for%20more%20than%201.4%20billion%20people%20at%20a%20very%20low%20cost.%26quot%3B%20This%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20built%20around%20an%20open%20and%20accessible%20network.%20It%20has%20regulations%20and%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20applications%20in%20order%20to%20modernise%20our%20economy%2C%20reform%20governance%2C%20and%20transform%20the%20lives%20of%20our%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20digital%20commerce%20democratic%20and%20accessible%20to%20all.%20This%20vision%20is%20the%20foundation%20of%20India's%20national%20AI%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20built%20an%20AI%20mission%20for%20good%2C%20and%20for%20all.%20Today%2C%20India%20leads%20in%20AI%20adaption%20and%20techno-legal%20solutions%20on%20data%20privacy.%20We%20are%20constantly%20developing%20AI%20applications%20for%20public%20good.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20India's%20pragmatic%20approach%20to%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20in%20good%20governance%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20AI%20talent%20pools.%20We%20are%20also%20building%20our%20own%20large%20language%20model%20in%20AI%20keeping%20in%20mind%20our%20diversity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20also%20has%20a%20unique%20public-private%20partnership%20model%20for%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20willing%20to%20share%20its%20experience%20and%20expertise%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20future%20of%20AI%20is%20for%20everyone%20on%20the%20planet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20at%20the%20dawn%20of%20the%20AI%20age%20that%20will%20shape%20the%20future%20of%20humanity.%20Some%20people%20worry%20about%20machines%20becoming%20superior%20to%20human%20beings%20in%20terms%20of%20intelligence%2C%20but%20noone%20holds%20the%20key%20to%20our%20collective%20future%20and%20shared%20destiny%20other%20than%20all%20of%20us%20-%20humans.%20That%20sense%20of%20responsibility%20is%20what%20must%20guide%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20and%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20co-chaired%20the%20AI%20Action%20Summit.%C2%A0The%20seminar%2C%20organised%20at%20the%20Grand%20Palais%20in%20Paris%2C%20saw%20participation%20by%20Heads%20of%20States%20and%20governments%2C%20leaders%20of%20international%20organisations%2C%20CEOs%20of%20small%20and%20large%20tech%20companies%2C%20representatives%20of%20academia%2C%20non-governmental%20organisations%2C%20artists%2C%20and%20members%20of%20civil%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20PM%20Modi%20congratulated%20President%20Macron%20for%20hosting%20the%20inaugural%20summit%20and%20said%20that%20India%20now%20looks%20forward%20to%20host%20the%20next%20AI%20Action%20Summit.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739274240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fi6gijtcs_pm-modi-ai-action-summit-afp_625x300_11_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fne