20that%20India%20has%20successfully%20built%20a%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%20for%20over%201.4%20billion%20at%20a%20very%20low%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20successfully%20built%20a%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%20for%20over%201.4%20billion%20people%20at%20a%20very%20low%20cost.%20It%20is%20built%20around%20an%20open%20and%20accessible%20network.%20It%20has%20regulations%20and%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20applications%20to%20modernise%20our%20economy%2C%20reform%20governance%20and%20transform%20the%20lives%20of%20our%20people...Today%2C%20India%20leads%20in%20AI%20adoption%20and%20techno-legal%20solutions%20on%20data%20privacy...We%20have%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20AI%20talent%20pools%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanking%20French%20President%20Emanual%20Macron%20for%20inviting%20him%20to%20co-chair%20the%20summit%2C%20PM%20Modi%20noted%2C%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20already%20reshaping%20our%20economy%2C%20security%20and%20even%20our%20society.%20AI%20is%20writing%20the%20code%20for%20humanity%20in%20this%20century...We%20are%20at%20the%20dawn%20of%20the%20AI%20age%20that%20will%20shape%20the%20course%20of%20humanity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20highlighted%20that%20India%20is%20building%20its%20own%20large%20language%20model%20considering%20its%20diversity%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20also%20have%20a%20unique%20public-private%20partnership%20model%20for%20pooling%20resources%20like%20compute%20power.%20It%20is%20made%20available%20to%20our%20startups%20and%20researchers%20at%20an%20affordable%20cost.%20India%20is%20ready%20to%20share%20its%20experience%20and%20expertise%20to%20ensure%20that%20AI%20future%20is%20for%20good%20and%20for%20all...Some%20people%20worry%20about%20machines%20becoming%20superior%20in%20intelligence%20to%20humans.%20But%20no%20one%20holds%20the%20key%20to%20our%20collective%20future%20and%20shared%20destiny%20other%20than%20us%20humans.%20That%20sense%20of%20responsibility%20must%20guide%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20spoke%20about%20democratising%20the%20technology%20and%20creating%20a%20sense%20of%20trust%20and%20transparency%20when%20developing%20open%20source%20systems%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20must%20develop%20open%20source%20systems%20that%20enhance%20trust%20and%20transparency.%20We%20must%20build%20quality%20data%20centres%20free%20from%20biases%2C%20we%20must%20democratise%20technology%20and%20create%20people%20centre%20applications.%20We%20must%20address%20concerns%20related%20to%20cyber%20security%2C%20disinformation%20and%20deepfakes.%20We%20must%20also%20ensure%20that%20technology%20is%20rooted%20in%20local%20ecosystems%20for%20it%20to%20be%20effective%20and%20useful.%20Loss%20of%20jobs%20is%20AI's%20most%20feared%20disruption%2C%20but%20history%20has%20shown%20that%20work%20does%20not%20disappear%20due%20to%20technology%2C%20only%20its%20nature%20changes.%20We%20need%20to%20invest%20in%20skilling%20and%20re-skilling%20our%20people%20for%20an%20AI-driven%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20addressed%20how%20fast%20AI%20is%20developing%20and%20suggested%20the%20need%20for%20collective%20global%20efforts%20to%20tackle%20risks%2C%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20developing%20at%20an%20unprecedented%20scale%20and%20speed%20and%20being%20adapted%20and%20deployed%20even%20faster.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20deep%20interdependence%20across%20borders.%20Therefore%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20collective%20global%20efforts%20to%20establish%20governance%20and%20standards%20that%20upload%20our%20shared%20values%2C%20address%20risks%2C%20and%20build%20trust.%20But%20governance%20is%20not%20just%20about%20managing%20rifts%20and%20rivalries.%20It%20is%20also%20about%20promoting%20innovation%20and%20deploying%20it%20for%20the%20global%20good.%20So%20we%20must%20think%20deeply%20and%20discuss%20openly%20about%20innovation%20and%20governance...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20emphasised%20that%20AI%20should%20be%20accessible%20to%20all%2C%20%26quot%3BGovernance%20is%20also%20about%20ensuring%20access%20to%20all%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Global%20South.%20It%20is%20where%20the%20capabilities%20are%20most%20lacking%20be%20it%20power%2C%20talent%2C%20or%20data%20for%20the%20financial%20resources.%20AI%20can%20help%20transform%20millions%20of%20lives%20by%20improving%20health%2C%20education%2C%20agriculture%20and%20so%20much%20more.%20It%20can%20help%20create%20a%20world%20in%20which%20the%20journey%20to%20sustainable%20development%20goals%20becomes%20easier%20and%20faster.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20we%20must%20pull%20together%20resources%20and%20talent.%20We%20must%20develop%20open-source%20systems%20that%20enhance%20trust%20and%20transparency.%20We%20must%20build%20quality%20data%20sets%20free%20from%20biases...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20in%20India's%20perspective%20and%20said%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20India%20leads%20in%20AI%20adoption%20and%20techno-legal%20solutions%20on%20data%20privacy...We%20have%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20AI%20talent%20pools...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Modi%20pointed%20out%20finally%20that%20conservation%20of%20energy%20is%20the%20key%20for%20the%20future%20of%20AI.%20He%20gave%20the%20example%20of%20a%20human%20brain%20and%20drew%20parallels%20saying%20that%20the%20way%20a%20human%20brain%20can%20do%20everything%20ranging%20from%C2%A0poetry%20to%20complex%20mathematics%2C%20at%20the%20fraction%20of%20the%20energy%20needed%20by%20a%20light%20bulb%2C%20is%20what%20the%20AI%20revolution%20must%20aim%20for.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739272620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Feqdmdg7_pm-modi-ai-summit-afp_625x300_11_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwe-are-in-dawn-of-ai-age-pm-narendra-modis-top-quotes-at-2025-paris-ai-summit-7685260%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hailing%20the%20development%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20