e%20rising.%20The%20World%20Health%20Organization%20reported%20a%2071%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20cholera%20deaths%20worldwide%20in%202023%2C%20with%20Africa%20experiencing%20a%20125%20per%20cent%20surge%20in%20cases%2C%20highlighting%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20improved%20sanitation%20and%20healthcare%20responses.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcholera-outbreak-kills-more-than-100-in-angola-ministry%2Farticleshow%2F118144218.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcholera-outbreak-kills-more-than-100-in-angola-ministry%2Famp_articleshow%2F118144218.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcholera-outbreak-kills-more-than-100-in-angola-ministry%2Famp_articleshow%2F118144218.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20CCTVs%20At%20Mumbai%20Studio%20Didn't%20Capture%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia's%20Crass%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia's%20crass%20remarks%20at%20India's%20Most%20Latent%20roast%20show%20as%20the%20camera%20was%20covered%20with%20a%20black%20cloth%20before%20the%20shoot%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20Mumbai%20Police%20made%20the%20startling%20revelation%20after%20it%20started%20probing%20complaints%20linked%20to%20Allahbadia's%20remarks%20that%20have%20sparked%20a%20nationwide%20debate%20on%20mature%20content%20in%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20a%20police%20team%20today%20visited%20The%20Habitat%20cafe%20in%20Khar%20West%20where%20the%20episode%20was%20shot.%20This%20cafe%20serves%20as%20a%20key%20venue%20for%20comedy%20shows%20and%20is%20owned%20by%20Balraj%20Singh%20Ghai.%20Mr%20Ghai%20is%20a%20friend%20of%20comic%20Samay%20Raina%2C%20who%20hosts%20India's%20Got%20Latent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20asked%20The%20Habitat%20authorities%20for%20details%20about%20the%20controversial%20episode%20and%20its%20CCTV%20footage.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20they%20found%20that%20during%20most%20shoots%2C%20the%20CCTV%20cameras%20are%20covered%20with%20a%20black%20cloth%20so%20they%20are%20not%20captured%20on%20CCTVs.%20Those%20who%20shoot%20these%20episodes%20take%20the%20content%20with%20them%20after%20the%20shooting.%20So%2C%20the%20studio%20does%20not%20have%20any%20record%20of%20what%20was%20shot.%20Covering%20CCTVs%20during%20shoots%20is%20a%20common%20practice%20among%20those%20recording%20content%20for%20YouTube%20to%20ensure%20it%20does%20not%20get%20leaked%20from%20the%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20video%20of%20the%20controversial%20remark%20has%20been%20removed%20from%20YouTube%20after%20the%20Centre%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20streaming%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Police%20have%20received%20multiple%20complaints%20over%20Allahbadia's%20crass%20remarks%20and%20are%20investigating%20the%20matter%20under%20Section%20173%20(3)%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagrarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita.%20Under%20this%20section%2C%20cops%20have%20to%20probe%20within%2014%20days%20if%20there%20is%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20and%20proceed%20accordingly.%20Assam%20Police%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20already%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20Allahbadia%2C%20Raina%2C%20influencer%20Apoorva%20Makhija%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllahbadia%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20BeerBiceps%20Guy%2C%20recently%20appeared%20in%20an%20episode%20of%20India's%20Got%20Latent%20hosted%20by%20Raina.%20A%20short%20clip%20from%20the%20show%2C%20which%20is%20now%20viral%2C%20shows%20Allahbadia%20asking%20a%20contestant%2C%20%26quot%3BWould%20you%20rather%20watch%20your%20parents%20have%20sex%20every%20day%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20life%20or%20join%20in%20once%20and%20stop%20it%20forever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%