cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fworld-leaders-seek-elusive-ai-common-ground-at-paris-summit%2Famp_articleshow%2F118142676.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fworld-leaders-seek-elusive-ai-common-ground-at-paris-summit%2Famp_articleshow%2F118142676.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%20Team%20Gujarat%20Titans%20Get%20New%20Owners%2C%20Majority%20Shares%20To%20Be%20Sold%20To...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20IPL%20champions%20Gujarat%20Titans%20are%20set%20to%20have%20new%20owners%20as%20Indian%20business%20conglomerate%2C%20the%20Torrent%20Group%2C%20is%20in%20line%20to%20acquire%20a%20majority%20stake%20in%20the%20franchise.%20The%20Ahmedabad-based%20conglomerate%20will%20purchase%20a%2067%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20the%20team%20from%20CVC%20Capital%20Partners%20(Irelia%20Company%20Pvt%20Ltd)%2C%20who%20had%20bought%20the%20team%20in%202021.%20The%20deal%20is%20awaiting%20final%20approval%20from%20the%20IPL%20governing%20council%2C%20which%20would%20allow%20Torrent%20Group%20to%20take%20control%20ahead%20of%20the%20upcoming%20season%2C%20which%20will%20begin%20on%20March%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20talks%20of%20Torrent%20Group%20taking%20two%20third%20ownership%20(67%20per%20cent)%20is%20at%20an%20advanced%20stage.%20The%20lock-in%20period%20for%20CVC%20group%20as%20sole%20owners%20ends%20in%20February%202025%20after%20which%20they%20are%20free%20to%20sell%20the%20stakes%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20IPL%20source%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTorrent%20group%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20Pharmaceutical%20sector%20in%20India%20and%20in%202021%20when%20BCCI%20invited%20bids%20for%20two%20new%20teams%2C%20they%20had%20shown%20active%20interest.%20Obviously%20any%20change%20in%20ownership%20pattern%20requires%20approval%20from%20BCCI%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20given%20in%20coming%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20valuation%20of%20the%20stake%20being%20sold%20by%20CVC%20remains%20unconfirmed%2C%20the%20global%20private%20equity%20firm%20had%20invested%20Rs%205%2C625%20crore%20to%20acquire%20the%20Titans%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20leadership%20of%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20the%20team%20clinched%20the%20title%20in%202022%20and%20signed%20off%20with%20a%20runner-up%20finish%20in%202023.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20last%20season%2C%20the%20Shubman%20Gill-led%20side%20finished%20in%20eighth%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20Gill%2C%20other%20key%20players%20in%20the%20team%20include%20Afghanistan%20spinner%20Rashid%20Khan%2C%20England%20white-ball%20captain%20Jos%20Buttler%2C%20and%20India%20pacer%20Mohammed%20Siraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETorrent%20Group%2C%20which%20boasts%20a%20valuation%20of%20approximately%20Rs%2041%2C000%20crore%2C%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20make%20inroads%20into%20the%20cricketing%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20its%20subsidiary%2C%20Torrent%20Sports%20Ventures%20Private%20Limited%2C%20it%20had%20previously%20bid%20for%20the%20Ahmedabad%20(Rs%204%2C653%20crore)%20and%20Lucknow%20(Rs%204%2C356%20crore)%20franchises%20in%202021%2C%20when%20the%20BCCI%20held%20an%20auction%20for%20two%20new%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20the%20group%20also%20made%20an%20unsuccessful%20attempt%20to%20acquire%20one%20of%20the%20three%20cities%20up%20for%20grabs%20in%20the%20inaugural%20Women's%20Premier%20League%20(WPL).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739266320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F2g9tging_shubman-gill-ipl_625x300_11_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fownership-change-at-gujarat-titans-majori