show%2C%20India's%20Got%20Latent.%20The%20accused%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20promoting%20obscenity%20and%20engaging%20in%20sexually%20explicit%20discussions%2C%20sparking%20massive%20public%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mukhija%2C%20known%20as%20'Rebel%20Kid'%20or%20'Kaleshi%20Aurat'%2C%20appeared%20as%20a%20guest%20panellist%20alongside%20Mr%20Allahbadia%2C%20Ashish%20Chanchlani%2C%20Jaspreet%20Singh%2C%20and%20host%20Samay%20Raina.%20During%20the%20episode%2C%20she%20made%20a%20vulgar%20remark%20involving%20a%20contestant's%20mother%2C%20drawing%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20viewers.%20While%20the%20show%20is%20known%20for%20its%20no-holds-barred%20humour%2C%20many%20believe%20this%20episode%20went%20too%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Ranveer%20Allahbadia's%20comments%20have%20been%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20controversy%2C%20Ms%20Mukhija's%20remarks%20have%20also%20caused%20outrage.%20Amid%20growing%20backlash%2C%20she%20posted%20a%20screenshot%20of%20a%20private%20chat%20with%20a%20friend%2C%20writing%2C%20%26quot%3BMe%20and%20%5Bfriend%5D's%20last%202%20brain%20cells%20trying%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20solve%20for%20the%20new%20problem%20that%20I%20created.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Apoorva%20Mukhija%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%202001%2C%20Apoorva%20Mukhija%20is%20a%20social%20media%20influencer%20with%20over%202.7%20million%20followers%20on%20Instagram.%20She%20is%20well-known%20for%20her%20mini%20vlogs%2C%20candid%20storytelling%20style%2C%20and%20content%20on%20lifestyle%2C%20fashion%2C%20and%20travel%20vlogs.%20She%20studied%20at%20Delhi%20Public%20School%2C%20Panipat%2C%20and%20the%20Convent%20of%20Jesus%20and%20Mary%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20She%20holds%20a%20B.Tech%20in%20Computer%20Engineering%20from%20Manipal%20University%2C%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mukhija%20is%20an%20Associate%20Sales%20Engineer%20Analyst%20at%20Dell%20Technologies%2C%20as%20per%20her%20LinkedIn%20profile.