ionaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20of%20Punjab%20MLAs%20at%20the%20national%20capital's%20Kapurthala%20House%20had%20attracted%20attention%2C%20with%20a%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20claiming%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20trying%20to%20replace%20Mr%20Mann%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20Manjinder%20Singh%20Sirsa%2C%20newly%20elected%20MLA%20from%20Rajouri%20Garden%2C%20claimed%20in%20a%20video%20that%20the%20AAP%20national%20convener%20was%20trying%20to%20remove%20Mr%20Mann%20by%20branding%20him%20%26quot%3Bincompetent%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20losing%20the%20Delhi%20elections%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20called%20a%20meeting%20of%20Punjab%20MLAs%20in%20Delhi.%20Reports%20suggest%20that%20he%20is%20trying%20to%20remove%C2%A0%40BhagwantMann%20Ji%20from%20the%20CM%20post%20by%20branding%20him%20as%20incompetent.%20He%20failed%20to%20fulfill%20his%20promise%20of%20giving%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20women%2C%20was%20unsuccessful%20in%20curbing%20drug%20abuse%20and%20has%20worsened%20Punjab's%20situation.%20Now%2C%20he%20wants%20to%20put%20all%20failure%20on%20Bhagwant%20Mann.%20He%20is%20making%20AAP%20Punjab%20MLAs%20say%20that%20Kejriwal%20is%20a%20'good%20man'%20and%20should%20be%20made%20Chief%20Minister%20instead%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Mann%20was%20asked%20about%20this%20claim%2C%20he%20smiled%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLet%20them%20say%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20assured%20that%20the%20Punjab%20government%20would%20fulfill%20its%20promise%20of%20giving%20Rs%201%2C000%20every%20month%20to%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20responded%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Partap%20Singh%20Bajwa's%20claim%20that%20more%20than%2020%20AAP%20MLAs%20in%20Punjab%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20him.%20%26quot%3BPartap%20Bajwa%20has%20been%20saying%20this%20for%20nearly%20three%20years.%20Ask%20him%20to%20count%20the%20number%20of%20(Congress)%20MLAs%20in%20Delhi%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20mocking%20the%20Congress%20for%20its%20hat-trick%20of%20scoring%20zero%20seats%20in%20the%20Delhi%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20asked%20about%20Mr%20Bajwa's%20claims%20that%20he%20may%20quit%20AAP.%20%26quot%3BLet%20them%20talk.%20We%20have%20built%20this%20party%20with%20our%20blood%20and%20sweat.%20Actually%2C%20they%20have%20a%20culture%20of%20switching%20sides...%C2%A0One%20of%20their%20leaders%20was%20beating%20a%20dhol%20to%20celebrate%20AAP's%20defeat.%20Someone%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20was%20celebrating%20Congress's%20zero%20score%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20has%2093%20MLAs%20and%20the%20Congress%2016%20in%20the%20117-member%20Punjab%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mann%20also%20spoke%20about%20what%20was%20discussed%20in%20today's%20meeting.%20He%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20thanked%20AAP%20workers%20for%20grassroots%20work%20in%20the%20party's%20Delhi%20campaign.%20He%20said%20AAP%20worked%20a%20lot%20in%20Delhi%20but%20wins%20and%20losses%20are%20part%20of%20politics.%20%26quot%3BWe%20accept%20the%20people's%20mandate%20in%20Delhi%2C%20now%20we%20plan%20to%20make%20Punjab%20a%20model%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Mann%20said%20all%20the%20MLAs%20wanted%20to%20meet%20Mr%20Kejriwal%2C%20so%20they%20came%20to%20Delhi%20for%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20also%20spoke%20to%20Ludhiana%20Central%20MLA%20Ashok%20Prashar%20about%20what%20was%20discussed%20at%20the%20meeting.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20told%20us%20we%20must%20take%20the%20party%20forward%20in%20Punjab.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20change%20in%20Punjab%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Asked%20about%20the%20Congress's%20claim%20about%20AAP%20MLAs%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20must%20take%20care%2C%20what%20if%20the%20few%20they%20have%20come%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739265060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Foq3d8tm_