%2C%20and%20they%20share%20this%20space%20with%2060%20million%20people.%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20humans%20and%20tigers%20living%20near%20each%20other!%20The%20research%20team%20found%20that%20this%20special%20area%20covers%20about%201%2C38%2C200%20square%20kilometres%20of%20land%2C%20where%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F338189%2Fbest-national-park-wildlife-safaris-in-winter-adventure-travel-guide-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etigers%20roam%20freely%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20forests%2C%20grasslands%2C%20and%20even%20areas%20close%20to%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20study%20credits%20four%20core%20areas%20that%20helped%20India%20achieve%20this%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20was%20able%20to%20stop%20people%20from%20hunting%20tigers%20by%20having%20strict%20laws%20and%20forest%20guards%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20protected%20the%20places%20where%20tigers%20live%20by%20making%20special%20areas%20called%20reserves%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20country%20made%20sure%20tigers%20had%20enough%20food%20to%20eat%20by%20protecting%20deer%20and%20other%20animals%20that%20tigers%20hunt%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndia%20helped%20the%20people%20who%20live%20near%20tigers%20by%20giving%20them%20support%20and%20money%20if%20and%20when%20they%20faced%20problems%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadvendradev%20Vikramsinh%20Jhala%2C%20the%20study%E2%80%99s%20lead%20author%2C%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20think%20human%20densities%20are%20detrimental%20to%20conservation%20of%20large%20carnivores.%20But%20more%20than%20density%2C%20it%20is%20the%20attitude%20of%20people%20that%20matters.%E2%80%9D%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20despite%20having%20a%20lower%20population%20density%2C%20Malaysia%20has%20not%20successfully%20revived%20its%20tiger%20population%20due%20to%20different%20soc