%20the%20gap%20of%20procurement%20in%20the%20food%20industry.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20realisation%20sowed%20the%20seeds%20of%20their%20second%20venture%20%E2%80%94%20an%20innovative%20platform%20aimed%20at%20streamlining%20procurement%20in%20the%20hospitality%20sector%20named%20%E2%80%98Agrainz%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20built%20a%20website%20to%20manage%20the%20raw%20materials%20for%20restaurants%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Srinidhi%2C%20Dhanvita%E2%80%99s%20husband.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgrainz%20provided%20restaurants%20with%20calculations%20to%20determine%20the%20expected%20yield%20and%20minimise%20waste%20from%20their%20raw%20material%20purchases.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20preferred%20a%20one-stop%20solution%20for%20the%20suggestions%20we%20gave%2C%20and%20we%20eventually%20started%20supplying%20450%20gourmet%20products%20like%20cheese%20and%20other%20perishable%20goods%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dhanvita.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20venture%20was%20short-lived%20due%20to%20COVID-19%20and%20their%20perishable%20products%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20meet%20its%20consumers%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20demand%2C%20leading%20to%20financial%20losses%20for%20the%20founders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20tangible%20that%20truly%20made%20a%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srinidhi.%20This%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20Aecoz%20in%202020%2C%20a%20boot-strapped%20startup%20focused%20on%20sustainable%20packaging%20solutions%20for%20the%20food%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPackaging%20out%20of%20paper%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%202019%20plastic%20ban%20may%20not%20have%20achieved%20its%20full%20potential%2C%20it%20served%20as%20a%20valuable%20catalyst%20for%20the%20development%20of%20biodegradable%20packaging%20alternatives%20for%20these%20entrepreneurs.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20%E2%80%98EatFit%E2%80%99%20(a%20food%20outlet%20catering%20to%20your%20diet)%2C%20who%20asked%20for%20biodegradable%20packaging.%20We%20took%20the%20challenge%20seriously%20and%20with%20a%20little%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20were%20successful%20in%20creating%20a%20durable%20yet%20sustainable%20product%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dhanvita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAecoz%E2%80%99s%20paper%20packaging%20production%20begins%20with%20sourcing%20paper%20reels%20from%20ITC%3B%20%E2%80%9CThey%20supply%20about%2085-90%25%20of%20the%20paper%20we%20use%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Bharath%2C%20who%20oversees%20the%20manufacturing%20unit.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20reels%20are%20coated%20with%20a%20water-based%20barrier%2C%20making%20the%20paper%20suitable%20for%20food%20packaging.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-33_11zon-1738594282-500x598.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aecoz%20packaging%20with%20Ritz%20Carlton%20branding.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-33_11zon-1738594282-500x598.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-33_11zon-1738594282-251x300.jpg%20251w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-33_11zon-1738594282-150x180.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FAdobe-Express-file-33_11zon-1738594282.jpg%20620w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-402962%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22598%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20packaging%20made%20by%20Aecoz%20is%2098%25%20biodegradable%20in%20180%20days.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20aqueous%20coating%20on%20our%20products%20makes%20the%20packaging%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F270443%2Fchuk-biodegradable-compostable-waste-sugarcane-fibre-tableware%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E98%25%20biodegradable%20in%20180%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20certified%20by%20the%20Central%20Institute%20of%20Petrochemicals%20Engineering%20%26amp%3B%20Technology%20(CIPET)%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dhanvita.%20After%20the%20180%20day%20period%2C%20the%20products%20are%20100%25%20degradable%2C%20Dhanvita%20informs.%20The%20product%20has%20also%20received%20food%20grade%2C%20pollution%20and%20no-plastic%20certification%20from%20CIPET.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20reels%20are%20cut%20into%20blanks%20and%20formed%20into%20bowls.%20The%20bowls%20then%20pass%20through%20high-temperature%20coils%20reaching%20approximately%20350%C2%B0C%20to%20melt%20the%20coating%20and%20create%20a%20durable%2C%20heat-resistant%20product.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20machine%20operates%20at%20an%20impressive%20speed%2C%20producing%2040-45%20pieces%20per%20minute%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bharath%20informs.%20%E2%80%9CAecoz%20utilises%20specialised%20machines%20to%20produce%20various%20sizes%20from%2050%20ml%20to%201000%20ml%2C%20ensuring%20tha